      "[{\"insert\":\"Welcome to DiaryVault\"},{\"insert\":\": \",\"attributes\":{\"color\":\"#FF8E24AA\"}},{\"insert\":\"Your Personal Journaling Companion\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":2}},{\"insert\":\"We're \"},{\"insert\":\"delighted\",\"attributes\":{\"bold\":true,\"color\":\"#FF00ACC1\"}},{\"insert\":\" \",\"attributes\":{\"bold\":true}},{\"insert\":\"to have you onboard., and we're \"},{\"insert\":\"excited \",\"attributes\":{\"italic\":true,\"color\":\"#FF03A9F4\"}},{\"insert\":\"to be your trusted partner in capturing your thoughts, memories and moments 📝\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\\nExpress Yourself with Rich Text:\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":3}},{\"insert\":\"Our powerful rich text editor allows you to \"},{\"insert\":\"craft your entries \",\"attributes\":{\"bold\":true}},{\"insert\":\"just the way you envision them. Add \"},{\"insert\":\"images \",\"attributes\":{\"italic\":true,\"color\":\"#FF039BE5\",\"bold\":true}},{\"insert\":\"and \"},{\"insert\":\"videos \",\"attributes\":{\"italic\":true,\"color\":\"#FF039BE5\",\"bold\":true}},{\"insert\":\"📸\",\"attributes\":{\"color\":\"#FF039BE5\"}},{\"insert\":\" \",\"attributes\":{\"italic\":true,\"color\":\"#FF039BE5\",\"bold\":true}},{\"insert\":\"to give life to your words and relive your memories.\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\\nYour Data, Your Control:\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":3}},{\"insert\":\"Your privacy 🔏 matters to us. With DiaryVault your journal entries are securely stored in your own \"},{\"insert\":\"Google Drive \",\"attributes\":{\"color\":\"#FF00897B\",\"bold\":true}},{\"insert\":\"or \"},{\"insert\":\"Dropbox \",\"attributes\":{\"color\":\"#FF00897B\",\"bold\":true}},{\"insert\":\"account\"},{\"insert\":\". \"},{\"insert\":\"You retain complete ownership and over your data. \"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\\nOffline First Experience:\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":3}},{\"insert\":\"You can utilize the app to the fullist even when you're offline. The app requires internet connection only during the signup process and cloud backup. \\n\\nSay Goodbye to Lost Notes:\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":3}},{\"insert\":\"We've got your back. DiaryVault automatically saves your notes, so you don't have to worry about losing your precious thoughts. Write freely and we'll ensure your words are safe 💜.\\n\\nSeemless Cross-Device Sync: \"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":3}},{\"insert\":\"Whether you're using DiaryVault on one phone or multiple devices. Your data is always kept in sync 🔃. You can fully restore your data on a new device.\\n \\nQuick and Secure Access:\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":3}},{\"insert\":\"DiaryVault ensures the safety and security of your notes with \"},{\"insert\":\"fingerprint \",\"attributes\":{\"color\":\"#FF2962FF\",\"bold\":true}},{\"insert\":\"and \"},{\"insert\":\"PIN\",\"attributes\":{\"color\":\"#FF2962FF\",\"bold\":true}},{\"insert\":\" based authentication 🔐, providing you with peace of mind and safeguarding your personal thoughts from prying eyes\\n\\nExport your Notes:\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":3}},{\"insert\":\"DiaryVault allows you to export your entries in the form of \"},{\"insert\":\"text files \",\"attributes\":{\"color\":\"#FF00ACC1\",\"bold\":true}},{\"insert\":\"and\"},{\"insert\":\" PDF\",\"attributes\":{\"color\":\"#FF00ACC1\",\"bold\":true}},{\"insert\":\". Share your thoughts easily with your friends or keep an offline copy for yourself.\\n\\nNever Miss a Day with Daily Reminders:\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":3}},{\"insert\":\"You can setup daily reminder \"},{\"insert\":\"notifications\",\"attributes\":{\"bold\":true,\"color\":\"#FFD500F9\"}},{\"insert\":\" to ensure you never miss a day of journaling.  Stay commited to your writing routine effortlessly 🔔✍️.\\n\\nPersonalize Your Experience:\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":3}},{\"insert\":\"Explore multiple themes, fonts, pen-colors to make your journal uniquely yours 🎠..\\n\\nListen to Your Notes:\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":3}},{\"insert\":\"DiaryVault offers Text-to-speech, enabling you to transform your written words into spoken ones. Sit back, relax and let your words come to life as you listen to your journals 🔊.\\n\\nYour Ad-free and Free of Cost Writing Journey:\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\",\"attributes\":{\"header\":3}},{\"insert\":\"We're dedicated to providing you with a precious writing journey that's entirely ad-free and free of cost. Our focus is on preserving the sanctity of your writing experience, ensuring no interruptions or hidden fees 💎🚫✍️.\\n\\n\"},{\"insert\":\"Happy Journaling 🎉\",\"attributes\":{\"italic\":true}},{\"insert\":\"\\nThe DiaryVault Team\\n\\n\"},{\"insert\":{\"image\":\"https://imgur.com/PumJ9nC.png\"}},{\"insert\":\"\\n\\n\\n\\n\"}]",
